 />\n<br />\n情節其實一般，但勝在角色立體，三者嘅互動精彩同深刻<br />\n運鏡、美術同配樂都好高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望奧斯卡會有好成績<br />\n<br />\n利申 好鍾意個導演"},{"pid":"4cea13f10c0ddb1ce2132648b9038bd7af6c79ba","tid":964400,"uid":27616,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T08:27:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WzHF3iH.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWzHF3iH.gif&h=7fef8b51&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d84e90d8a6381ff9dbb2b1704c50135f2b1e9d5e","tid":964400,"uid":88123,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T08:48:48.000Z","msg":"為左睇emma stone個角色"},{"pid":"a969e9ae5e9b01efa12a1d1605bc67374097e426","tid":964400,"uid":42624,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T09:48:37.000Z","msg":"比起個導演之前作品（一貫黑色荒唐風格），係The Favourite比較少，可以話商業化d。但仍可接受，個人覺得係劇本搭夠，同埋演員都做得好好，特別係呢d以三個角色為主導、軸心既戲。<br />\nbtw上youtube睇返d festival 記者會上casts同導演既sharing，對套戲既細節/內容會了解更多的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e70230b927a5a867b9f8b2cbf536f0dcb7dfcbb7","tid":964400,"uid":152432,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T09:56:12.000Z","msg":"自然光影真係好鬼靚"},{"pid":"6dc81ee3e33345c3fa3f360487155f5b0f346030","tid":964400,"uid":225102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T12:00:56.000Z","msg":"啲配樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ff4d99f410bf29e4802e37bb4f3add9794ccec8","tid":964400,"uid":28353,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"088e55a4d7ff726a16c9fde4e4a0525d239b3821","tid":964400,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fe6a5156c0a99ebfc5e6b769e0959aedd65221c","tid":964400,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"8650c82a9e338f19ed46d2f4a264298bdfe9efc0","tid":964400,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":2,"repl